name: TunnelFin
description: Privacy-first anonymous torrent streaming for Jellyfin via Tribler's IPv8 network. Stream torrents anonymously with multi-hop circuits, integrated content discovery, advanced filtering, and privacy-aware metrics.
overview: Anonymous torrent streaming with Tribler IPv8 network integration

versions.changelog:
v1.0.0.17 - E2E tests and Prowlarr validation:
- Added Prowlarr connectivity and configuration E2E tests
- Channel search fully functional with Prowlarr integration
- All 11 E2E tests passing

v1.0.0.16 - API search endpoint:
- Search via /TunnelFin/Search API endpoint
- Fixed version display in Jellyfin UI
- E2E tests updated to use API endpoint

v1.0.0.15 - Channel improvements:
- Fixed channel root to show helpful search instructions
- Added support for encoded search queries via folderId
- Improved logging for GetChannelItems

v1.0.0.14 - Assembly conflict fix:
- Excluded MonoTorrent.PortForwarding.dll to avoid Mono.Nat conflict with Jellyfin
- Using NullPortForwarder (port forwarding not needed for anonymous tunnel routing)
- Fixed plugin load failure on Jellyfin 10.11.5

v1.0.0.9 - Service registration fix:
- Added IChannel registration for TunnelFinChannel
- Registered ITorrentEngine, IStreamManager, IIndexerManager services
- Channel should now appear in Jellyfin UI

v1.0.0.8 - SDK version fix:
- Downgraded Jellyfin SDK from 10.11.5 to 10.11.4 to match server version
- Fixed assembly version mismatch causing plugin load failure
- Plugin should now load correctly on Jellyfin 10.11.4

v1.0.0.7 - IChannel interface fix:
- Fixed IRequiresMediaInfoCallback interface implementation
- Corrected GetChannelItemMediaInfo method signature
- Plugin should now load and register channel correctly

v1.0.0.6 - Plugin metadata fix:
- Added meta.json to plugin package for Jellyfin compatibility
- Fixed 'NotSupported' plugin status
- Plugin should now load correctly in Jellyfin

v1.0.0.5 - Service registration fix:
- Added IChannel registration for TunnelFinChannel
- Registered ITorrentEngine, IStreamManager, IIndexerManager services
- Fixed Jellyfin channel discovery
- Channel should now appear in Jellyfin Channels section

v1.0.0.4 - Plugin loading fix:
- Removed native runtime libraries that caused assembly loading errors
- Cleaned up unnecessary dependencies from plugin package
- Reduced package size from 25MB to 10MB

Previous features:
- Anonymous torrent streaming via Tribler IPv8 network
- Multi-hop circuit routing (1-3 hops)
- Integrated content discovery with Torznab indexers
- Advanced filtering (Required/Preferred/Excluded/Include)
- Multi-criteria sorting with custom orders
- Privacy-aware metrics and observability
- 90%+ test coverage
- Self-contained C# plugin

v1.0.0.1 - .NET 9.0 compatibility fix:
- Fixed .NET framework targeting for Jellyfin 10.11.x
- Rebuilt plugin DLL targeting .NET 9.0

Initial features:
- Anonymous torrent streaming via Tribler IPv8 network
- Multi-hop circuit routing (1-3 hops)
- Integrated content discovery with Torznab indexers
- Advanced filtering (Required/Preferred/Excluded/Include)
- Multi-criteria sorting with custom orders
- Privacy-aware metrics and observability
- 90%+ test coverage
- Self-contained C# plugin
